  SCIENCE FACTS
============================================================

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Newton's Second Law
Formula: F = ma
Note:    Force equals mass times acceleration; classical mechanics

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   1st Law of Thermodynamics
Formula: ΔU = Q - W
Note:    Energy conservation in thermodynamic systems

Domain:  Biology
Topic:   Natural Selection
Formula: Favorable traits lead to greater reproduction
Note:    Mechanism of evolution; Darwin 1859

Domain:  Astronomy
Topic:   Hubble's Law
Formula: v = H₀ × d
Note:    Universe is expanding; galaxies recede from us

Domain:  Astronomy
Topic:   Milky Way Size
Formula: ~100,000 light-years diameter
Note:    Our galaxy; contains 200-400 billion stars

============================================================
  DISEASES & MEDICINE
============================================================

Disease:     Tuberculosis
Type:        Bacterial
Pathogen:    M. tuberculosis
Transmission:Airborne droplets
Symptoms:    Persistent cough, night sweats
Treatment:   6-9 month antibiotics
Deaths/yr:   1.6M
Vaccine:     Yes (BCG, partial)
Discovered:  1882

Disease:     Ebola
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    Ebola virus
Transmission:Bodily fluids contact
Symptoms:    Fever, bleeding, organ failure
Treatment:   Monoclonal antibodies, supportive
Deaths/yr:   0.001M
Vaccine:     Yes (Ervebo for Zaire strain)
Discovered:  1976

Disease:     Smallpox
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    Variola
Transmission:Respiratory, contact
Symptoms:    Pockmarks, fever
Treatment:   Eradicated (1980)
Deaths/yr:   EradicatedM
Vaccine:     Yes
Discovered:  Antiquity

